you're a minute early.

01:32.893 --> 01:35.396
If you're early, you're on time.
If you're on time...

01:35.429 --> 01:37.165
You're late.

01:37.198 --> 01:39.567
Whoever taught you that
must have been very wise.

01:39.600 --> 01:40.734
Yeah, she's a'ight.

01:40.768 --> 01:42.636
So state your purpose.

