39:44.015 --> 39:45.917
Think she might have
drawn your name, Pride,

39:45.951 --> 39:48.787
because last I spoke with her,
she was feeling the pressure.

39:48.820 --> 39:50.856
Yeah, she may have even
cracked under it.

39:50.889 --> 39:53.925
I admit...

39:53.959 --> 39:55.761
I was feeling the stress,

39:55.794 --> 39:58.597
but then, I realized,

39:58.630 --> 40:02.100
the best gifts
are from the heart.

40:02.133 --> 40:04.903
So this is for you, King.

40:04.936 --> 40:07.873
Oh. This is gonna be good.

